  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To assess the effects of Acetyl-L-Carnitine, probiotics and antioxidant nutritional
      substances administration on work productivity, daily activity, and fatigue in subjects with
      chronic hepatitis C treated with Pegylated-Interferon-α2b and Ribavirin.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
